<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Our Educators</title>

  <!-- Bootstrap CSS and JS -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

  <%- include('partials/header.ejs') %>
</head>
  <%- include('partials/navbar1.ejs') %>
<body style="color: #1f11ea;">
 

  <div class="container my-4">
    <!-- Intro Section -->
    <h2 class="text-center">Meet Our Educators</h2>
    <br>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      At <strong>Tiny Treasures</strong>, our educators are caring, qualified, and passionate about helping every child feel safe, confident, and ready to learn.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      Each team member brings unique strengths to the classroom — from creative arts to outdoor exploration — while working closely with families to support every child’s development.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      We believe strong relationships, cultural respect, and joyful learning create the best start in life.
    </p>
    <!-- Educator Profiles Section -->
    <div class="row text-center mt-5">
      <!-- Educator 1 -->
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <img src="/images/asha.jpg" alt="Asha Minu" class="img-fluid rounded-circle"
        style="width: 200px; height: 200px; object-fit: cover;">
        <h5 class="mt-2">Asha Minu</h5>
        <p>Lead Educator<br><small>ECE Level 4</small></p>
        <p>Asha has over 15 years of experience in early childhood education, specializing in child-led learning and fostering a love for nature through outdoor play.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Educator 2 -->
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <img src="/images/jason.jpg" alt="Jason Lee" class="img-fluid rounded-circle"
        style="width: 200px; height: 200px; object-fit: cover;">
        <h5 class="mt-2">Jason Lee</h5>
        <p>ECE Teacher<br><small>Bachelor of Education</small></p>
        <p>With over 10 years of experience, Jason brings a calm, joyful presence to the classroom and is especially passionate about creative arts and sensory learning.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Educator 3 -->
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <img src="/images/aroha.jpg" alt="Aroha Williams" class="img-fluid rounded-circle"
        style="width: 200px; height: 200px; object-fit: cover;">
        <h5 class="mt-2">Aroha Williams</h5>
        <p>Kaiako Māori<br><small>ECE Qualified</small></p>
        <p>Aroha is dedicated to incorporating Māori culture and language into daily learning, fostering a strong sense of identity and belonging for all children.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

